<div class="hero" id="hero">
	<div class="hero__content">
    <img src="/images/marina-aisa-photo.png" class="hero__profile" alt="Marina Aisa Picture" />
    <div class="hero__text">
      <h1 id="hero-text"></h1>
    </div>
	</div>
</div>
<div id="portfolio" class="portfolio">
  <div class="portfolio__title">
    <h1>Design Portfolio <any emoji="writing-hand" emoji-tone="light"></any> <span class="portfolio__title--coming">– More coming soon</span></h1>
  </div>
  <div class="portfolio__content">
    <%= partial "partials/portfolio" %>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="about" id="about">
  <div class="about__container">
    <div class="about__title">
      <h1>About Marina <any emoji="thinking-face""></any></h1>
    </div>
    <div class="about__content">
      <p>I’m a <span class="about__content--important">Product Designer (UI/UX) and Front-End Developer</span> based in <span class="about__content--important">Barcelona</span>. I studied an engineering degree in Helsinki and Hong Kong, worked in big corporations and small startups and traveled to almost every capital in Europe and Asia. I'm interested in new technologies as VR, AR and blockchain, also in politics and feminism. My surname is Aragonese, as Zaragoza (Spain), where I was born 21 years ago with my two triplet brothers.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="experience">
  <div class="experience__container">
    <div class="experience__title">
      <h1>Work Experience <any emoji="woman-technologist"></any></h1>
    </div>
    <ul class="experience__content">
      <%= partial "partials/work-experience" %>
    </ul>
    <div class="experience__title">
      <h1>Education <any emoji="nerd-face"></any></h1>
    </div>
    <ul class="experience__content">
      <%= partial "partials/education-experience" %>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="call-to-action">
  <div class="call-to-action__container">
    <div class="call-to-action__image">
      <img src="images/professionals.png">
    </div>
    <div class="call-to-action__text">
      <p>
        If you want to know what other amazing <any emoji="two-hearts"></any> proffesionals that I admire and I have worked with think about me <any emoji="flushed-face"></any> , check my <a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/marinaaisa/" class="ani linkedin"><span>Linkedin</span></a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="map">
  <div class="map__container">
    <div class="map__title">
      <h1>Hobby: Discovering the world <any emoji="rocket"></h1>
    </div>
    <div class="map__content">
      <div class="map__text">
        <p>
          These are all the countries that I have <span class="map__text--visited">visited</span> or <span class="map__text--lived">lived in</span>.
          Poland and USA coming <any emoji="soon-arrow">
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="map__map">
        <div id="map"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="dribbble">
  <div class="dribbble__container">
    <p class="dribbble__text">
      If you want to check more designs that I have done,
      check my <a target="_blank" href="https://dribbble.com/MarinaAisa" class="ani dribbble"><span>Dribbble</span></a>.
    </p>
    <ul class="dribbble__posts"></ul>
  </div>
</div>
